 * style.section_padding_mobile => 区域内边距(移动端):number:48|px
 * style.card_gap => 卡片间距:number:24|px
 *
 * group:texts => 文本内容
 * texts.title => 区域标题:text:Why IPL Sunflare Feels Quicker
 * texts.kicker => 区域提示:text:IPL Sunflare Edge
 * texts.summary => 区域辅助文案:textarea:Every layer is tuned for faster room discovery, quicker match entry, and smoother repeat rounds.
 * texts.lead_chip => 主卡片提示:text:Speed Advantage
